arsening.\n  Applications to multi-dimensional persistence and crocker stacks are also\npresented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Apr 2021 23:06:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 02:39:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 31 May 2023 16:45:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
