 $V_K$. If $\\bar K$ is not\nextremely far from a Euclidean ball to begin with, an analogous isometric\nresult, where $8$ is replaced by $1+\\epsilon$, is obtained as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 09:06:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 09:38:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 23:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 11:30:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-02"}
