ally, we consider different jet launching times\nreferred to the same BNS merger model and discuss the consequences for the\nultimate jet properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 09:07:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2021 14:58:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-07"}
