atmospheric analysis of\nWASP-43b secondary eclipse data obtained from space- and ground-based\nobservations. We compare our results with the results from the literature, and\ninvestigate how the inclusion of additional opacity sources influence the\nbest-fit model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:48:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-27"}
