 a\nwater exosphere or significant excavation of surface features. The surface\nturnover rate from the micro-meteoroid populations considered is estimated to\nbe $1.25$ Myr on Ceres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 14:35:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-27"}
